{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"So there are a few things"},{"time":3000,"text":"that bring us humans together in the way that an election does."},{"time":6000,"text":"We stand in elections; we vote in elections;"},{"time":9000,"text":"we observe elections."},{"time":11000,"text":"Our democracies rely on elections."},{"time":14000,"text":"We all understand why we have elections,"},{"time":17000,"text":"and we all leave the house on the same day"},{"time":19000,"text":"to go and vote."},{"time":21000,"text":"We cherish the opportunity to have our say,"},{"time":24000,"text":"to help decide the future of the country."},{"time":29000,"text":"The fundamental idea is that politicians"},{"time":31000,"text":"are given mandate to speak for us,"},{"time":34000,"text":"to make decisions on our behalf"},{"time":36000,"text":"that affect us all."},{"time":38000,"text":"Without that mandate, they would be corrupt."}]},{"cues":[{"time":41000,"text":"Well unfortunately, power corrupts,"},{"time":43000,"text":"and so people will do lots of things"},{"time":46000,"text":"to get power and to stay in power,"},{"time":49000,"text":"including doing bad things to elections."},{"time":53000,"text":"You see, even if the idea"},{"time":55000,"text":"of the election is perfect,"},{"time":57000,"text":"running a countrywide election is a big project,"},{"time":60000,"text":"and big projects are messy."},{"time":63000,"text":"Whenever there is an election,"},{"time":65000,"text":"it seems like something always goes wrong,"},{"time":67000,"text":"someone tries to cheat,"},{"time":69000,"text":"or something goes accidentally awry --"},{"time":72000,"text":"a ballot box goes missing here,"},{"time":75000,"text":"chads are left hanging over here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":78000,"text":"To make sure as few things as possible go wrong,"},{"time":82000,"text":"we have all these procedures around the election."},{"time":85000,"text":"So for example, you come to the polling station,"},{"time":88000,"text":"and a poll station worker asks for your ID"},{"time":91000,"text":"before giving you a ballot form"},{"time":93000,"text":"and asking you to go into a voting booth"},{"time":95000,"text":"to fill out your vote."},{"time":97000,"text":"When you come back out, you get to drop your vote"},{"time":99000,"text":"into the ballot box"},{"time":101000,"text":"where it mixes with all the other votes,"},{"time":103000,"text":"so that no one knows how you voted."}]},{"cues":[{"time":106000,"text":"Well, what I want us to think about for a moment"},{"time":108000,"text":"is what happens after that,"},{"time":110000,"text":"after you drop your vote into the ballot box."},{"time":112000,"text":"And most people would go home"},{"time":114000,"text":"and feel sure that their vote has been counted,"},{"time":116000,"text":"because they trust"},{"time":118000,"text":"that the election system works."},{"time":120000,"text":"They trust that election workers and election observers"},{"time":123000,"text":"do their jobs and do their jobs correctly."},{"time":127000,"text":"The ballot boxes go to counting places."},{"time":130000,"text":"They're unsealed and the votes are poured out"},{"time":133000,"text":"and laboriously counted."},{"time":136000,"text":"Most of us have to trust"},{"time":138000,"text":"that that happens correctly for our own vote,"},{"time":140000,"text":"and we all have to trust that that happens correctly"},{"time":143000,"text":"for all the votes in the election."},{"time":146000,"text":"So we have to trust a lot of people."},{"time":150000,"text":"We have to trust a lot of procedures."},{"time":154000,"text":"And sometimes we even have to trust computers."},{"time":159000,"text":"So imagine hundreds of millions of voters"},{"time":161000,"text":"casting hundreds of millions of votes,"},{"time":163000,"text":"all to be counted correctly"},{"time":166000,"text":"and all the things that can possibly go wrong"},{"time":169000,"text":"causing all these bad headlines,"},{"time":174000,"text":"and you cannot help but feel exhausted at the idea"},{"time":177000,"text":"of trying to make elections better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":183000,"text":"Well in the face of all these bad headlines,"},{"time":185000,"text":"researchers have taken a step back"},{"time":188000,"text":"and thought about how we can do elections differently."},{"time":192000,"text":"They've zoomed out and looked at the big picture."},{"time":195000,"text":"And the big picture is this:"},{"time":197000,"text":"elections should be verifiable."},{"time":201000,"text":"Voters should be able to check"},{"time":204000,"text":"that their votes are counted correctly,"},{"time":207000,"text":"without breaking election secrecy,"},{"time":209000,"text":"which is so very important."},{"time":212000,"text":"And that's the tough part."},{"time":214000,"text":"How do we make an election system completely verifiable"},{"time":217000,"text":"while keeping the votes"},{"time":219000,"text":"absolutely secret?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":221000,"text":"Well, the way we've come up with"},{"time":223000,"text":"uses computers"},{"time":225000,"text":"but doesn't depend on them."},{"time":227000,"text":"And the secret is the ballot form."},{"time":229000,"text":"And if you look closely at these ballot forms,"},{"time":231000,"text":"you'll notice that the candidate list"},{"time":233000,"text":"is in a different order on each one."},{"time":235000,"text":"And that means, if you mark your choices on one of them"},{"time":238000,"text":"and then remove the candidate list,"},{"time":240000,"text":"I won't be able to tell from the bit remaining"},{"time":243000,"text":"what your vote is for."},{"time":246000,"text":"And on each ballot form there is this encrypted value"},{"time":249000,"text":"in the form of this 2D barcode"},{"time":251000,"text":"on the right."},{"time":253000,"text":"And there's some complicated cryptography"},{"time":255000,"text":"going on in there,"},{"time":257000,"text":"but what's not complicated"},{"time":259000,"text":"is voting with one of these forms."},{"time":262000,"text":"So we can let computers do all the complicated cryptography for us,"},{"time":265000,"text":"and then we'll use the paper for verification."}]},{"cues":[{"time":269000,"text":"So this is how you vote."},{"time":271000,"text":"You get one of these ballot forms at random,"},{"time":275000,"text":"and then you go into the voting booth,"},{"time":277000,"text":"and you mark your choices,"},{"time":279000,"text":"and you tear along a perforation."},{"time":284000,"text":"And you shred the candidate list."},{"time":287000,"text":"And the bit that remains, the one with your marks --"},{"time":290000,"text":"this is your encrypted vote."},{"time":292000,"text":"So you let a poll station worker"},{"time":294000,"text":"scan your encrypted vote."},{"time":296000,"text":"And because it's encrypted,"},{"time":298000,"text":"it can be submitted, stored"},{"time":300000,"text":"and counted centrally"},{"time":303000,"text":"and displayed on a website"},{"time":305000,"text":"for anyone to see, including you."},{"time":308000,"text":"So you take this encrypted vote"},{"time":311000,"text":"home as your receipt."},{"time":313000,"text":"And after the close of the election,"},{"time":315000,"text":"you can check that your vote was counted"},{"time":317000,"text":"by comparing your receipt"},{"time":320000,"text":"to the vote on the website."},{"time":324000,"text":"And remember, the vote is encrypted"},{"time":326000,"text":"from the moment you leave the voting booth,"},{"time":329000,"text":"so if an election official wants to find out how you voted,"},{"time":332000,"text":"they will not be able to."},{"time":334000,"text":"If the government wants to find out how you voted,"},{"time":336000,"text":"they won't be able to."},{"time":339000,"text":"No hacker can break in"},{"time":341000,"text":"and find out how you voted."},{"time":343000,"text":"No hacker can break in and change your vote,"},{"time":346000,"text":"because then it won't match your receipt."},{"time":349000,"text":"Votes can't go missing"},{"time":352000,"text":"because then you won't find yours when you look for it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":356000,"text":"But the election magic doesn't stop there."},{"time":359000,"text":"Instead, we want to make the whole process"},{"time":361000,"text":"so transparent"},{"time":363000,"text":"that news media and international observers"},{"time":366000,"text":"and anyone who wants to"},{"time":368000,"text":"can download all the election data"},{"time":370000,"text":"and do the count themselves."},{"time":372000,"text":"They can check that all the votes were counted correctly."},{"time":375000,"text":"They can check"},{"time":377000,"text":"that the announced result of the election"},{"time":379000,"text":"is the correct one."},{"time":381000,"text":"And these are elections"},{"time":383000,"text":"by the people, for the people."},{"time":385000,"text":"So the next step for our democracies"},{"time":388000,"text":"are transparent"},{"time":390000,"text":"and verifiable elections."}]},{"cues":[{"time":392000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":394000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}